332
00:30:47,846 --> 00:30:50,544
He was a satanist.
Richard Reeves.

333
00:30:50,718 --> 00:30:53,068
Richard Joshua Reeves.
He killed 13 people.

334
00:30:53,242 --> 00:30:54,548
Similar profile.

335
00:30:54,722 --> 00:30:56,593
We're aware.

336
00:30:56,767 --> 00:30:59,379
Those kind of satanic symbols
