356
00:32:12,104 --> 00:32:12,887
Explosives?

357
00:32:13,061 --> 00:32:14,454
Dynamite.

358
00:32:14,933 --> 00:32:18,066
About 20 pounds or so
of old-school, volatile TNT.

359
00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:20,895
Enough to do
significant damage.

360
00:32:23,332 --> 00:32:24,855
Manson and "The Family,"

361
