Slasher,
killing all those people.

372
00:33:08,116 --> 00:33:10,901
When this is over, you wanna
know who's gonna be behind it?

373
00:33:11,119 --> 00:33:12,555
The government.

374
00:33:12,773 --> 00:33:14,731
I read on 8chan
how our government,

375
00:33:14,949 --> 00:33:17,604
